rows.label: qst105408_msg0001
rows.name:
You come to see legendary treasure
too?

rows.label: qst105408_msg0002
rows.name:
This Calamity Puzzle! Incredible!
Astounding!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0003
rows.name:
Zubzub finally make dream of
salvagers around world reality!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0004
rows.name:
You had fill of staring? Then
Zubzub go to sell treasure at
Central Exchange now.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0005
rows.name: Mehmeh? You want Calamity Puzzle?

rows.label: qst105408_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, Zubzub planning to sell
anyway, and it heavy to carry around,
so not actual worst idea.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0007
rows.name: Selling for 500,000G.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0008
rows.name:
Not see why friends surprised.
It reasonable going rate.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0009
rows.name:
Had to wait super long time until Divine Beast
in exact position...

rows.label: qst105408_msg0010
rows.name:
then lift up using expensive gas
cylinders and crazy-good wire.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0011
rows.name:
Zubzub not sell for less or else not
turn out profit.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0013
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: qst105408_msg0014
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst105408_msg0101
rows.name: One, two, three... 500,000G, all there!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0102
rows.name: Calamity Puzzle all yours!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0103
rows.name:
It extremely heavy, so friends
be careful when carrying.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0104
rows.name:
Would have cost Zubzub 5,000G
to carry to Central Exchange, so was
big big help!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0105
rows.name:
Okay, Zubzub return to treasure hunting
now. Thanks much again for purchase!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0201
rows.name:
If friends not purchase, then Zubzub
heading out to sell.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0202
rows.name:
But not want to lug all way there, so
can wait for friends to prepare money.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0301
rows.name:
If friends looking to purchase Calamity
Puzzle, will be 500,000G.
